    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices: 
        - Report Info: Feature comparison (Users, Inventory, Credit, Reports, Support).
        - Goal: Visually compare Beta vs. Pro versions to highlight Pro's superior value.
        - Viz/Presentation Method: 
            1. Side-by-side cards (HTML/Tailwind) for direct feature comparison.
            2. Radar Chart (Chart.js/Canvas) for a holistic, multi-dimensional view of feature completeness.
        - Interaction: The chart is dynamic and responsive. Cards and buttons have hover states for user feedback.
        - Justification: The radar chart offers an immediate, impactful visualization of the feature gap, which is more effective than text alone. The card layout is modern and responsive.
        - Library/Method: Chart.js for the chart, HTML/Tailwind for the layout.
    -->

